    "description": "<p>Activates when all of your [hand slots] are empty. Your bare-handed [Attack Power] and [Magic Power] are [CR + ([INT Mod] x 2)]. You get 1 [Illusion Weapon] tag at the start of the scene. This tag is lost at the end of the scene. </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>(SR2) Also get 1 tag at the start of setup in the 2nd and subsequent rounds. </p>\n<p>(SR3) You always get [Cancel: Number of [Illusion Weapon] tags x 5].</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A fighting style in which one creates numerous weapons using genjutsu and manipulates them freely.</p>",
